# ── HopMap Agent overrides ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Operational config lives in agent_config.json (edit that for most settings).
# Only put per-machine overrides here that shouldn't be in the repo.
# Copy this to .env if needed. Never commit .env to git.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Example: override the server URL for a specific machine without editing the JSON
# HOPMAP_AGENT_BACKEND_URL=http://192.168.1.10:8000